<MELItem itemNbr="22-31-01" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-22-31-01.1.2-22-31-01">
<Title>Autothrottle System</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>EEC normal mode operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Approach minimums do not require its use.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>EDTO beyond 180 minutes is not conducted.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
<Note>
<Para>Any mode which operates normally may be used.</Para>
</Note>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationNote>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Maximum landing capability is CAT IIIA.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Some failure modes of the autothrottle system may cause the thrust reference/target indications to be inoperative.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</OperationNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
